subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Scott Simpson matched the lowest round of the tournament with a six-under-par 66 and held a two-shot lead over David Edwards after two rounds of the Boeing Classic at the T.P.C. Snoqualmie Ridge in Snoqualmie, Wash. Simpson made five birdies on the back nine.
